        "from": "SQS Queue",
        "to": "Failed Messages",
        "status": "broken",
        "issue": "No dead-letter queue configured. Poison messages (corrupt images, unsupported formats, oversized files) will retry infinitely, consuming worker capacity and compounding the throughput deficit."
