    "contract_compliance": "SQS consumer contract is fundamentally broken: the worker cannot meet the throughput SLA implied by the inbound rate, and the visibility timeout is misconfigured relative to batch processing time.",
    "data_flow_integrity": "Messages will be processed multiple times due to visibility timeout expiry mid-batch. Any non-idempotent side effects (e.g., image stored twice, webhooks fired twice, billing events duplicated) will cause data integrity issues."
